OL,3,CMedicines regulator to approve
OL,4,CAlzheimer's drug shown to slow disease
OL,6,FA drug which has been proven to slow
OL,7,Fthe progression of Alzheimer's disease
OL,8,Fis to receive approval from the UK's
OL,9,Fmedicines regulator.
OL,11,FLecanemab, developed by pharmaceutical
OL,12,Fcompany Eisai, is a targeted antibody
OL,13,Ftreatment that binds to amyloid, a
OL,14,Fprotein which builds up in the brains
OL,15,Fof people living with Alzheimer's
OL,16,Fdisease.
