OL,3,CMedicines regulator to approve
OL,4,CAlzheimer's drug shown to slow disease
OL,6,FThe drug is designed to help clear the
OL,7,Fbuild-up and slow down cognitive
OL,8,Fdecline in people with the condition
OL,9,Fand is given to patients via an
OL,10,Fintravenous drip fortnightly.
OL,12,FA decision from the Medicines and
OL,13,FHealthcare products Regulatory Agency
OL,14,F(MHRA) is expected to be announced
OL,15,Fshortly, but it is understood to have
OL,16,Fapproved the treatment.
