OL,3,CMedicines regulator to approve
OL,4,CAlzheimer's drug shown to slow disease
OL,6,FFurther signoff will be needed from
OL,7,Fthe National Institute for Health and
OL,8,FCare Excellence (Nice) - the health
OL,9,Fservice spending watchdog - before it
OL,10,Fis rolled out on the NHS in England.
OL,12,FLecanemab is already licensed in the
OL,13,FUnited States, where it costs about
OL,14,F#20,000 per patient per year, although
OL,15,Fit was rejected by the European
OL,16,FMedicines Agency (EMA) in late July.
