OL,6,FNHS England estimates between 50,000
OL,7,Fand 280,000 patients might be eligible
OL,8,Ffor the new treatments.
OL,10,FPrior to being given the drugs, they
OL,11,Fwill need to have a baseline MRI scan
OL,12,Fand then either a Pet-CT scan or
OL,13,Flumbar puncture to confirm Alzheimer's.
